1
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,000
Soldiers,

2
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:19,920
we are the sons of Great Yan!

3
00:00:20,350 --> 00:00:22,750
Born on the grasslands,
we stand above all!

4
00:00:23,070 --> 00:00:25,200
Now, Biantang has broken its promise,

5
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:27,120
failing to return our Queen

6
00:00:27,870 --> 00:00:30,550
and trampling on our dignity and glory!

7
00:00:31,350 --> 00:00:32,070
Today,

8
00:00:32,430 --> 00:00:36,090
the Black Eagle Army's cavalry
shall raze Biantang to the ground!

9
00:00:37,110 --> 00:00:38,430
Raze Biantang to the ground!

10
00:00:38,430 --> 00:00:39,900
Long live Great Yan!

11
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:42,790
Raze Biantang to the ground!
Long live Great Yan!

12
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:45,750
Raze Biantang to the ground!
Long live Great Yan!

13
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:48,570
Raze Biantang to the ground!
Long live Great Yan!

14
00:02:08,530 --> 00:02:13,500
[REBIRTH]

15
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:16,530
[Episode 20]

16
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:23,520
Your Majesty,

17
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,520
an urgent report.

18
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:26,910
Your Majesty,

19
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,070
Yan Xun, King of Great Yan,

20
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:30,280
has declared war on us
under the pretext that we're harboring

21
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,470
his queen, Chu Qiao!

22
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:32,800
He's already broken through
three cities in a row,

23
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,500
and the army is now
bearing down on Longyin Pass.

24
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:37,190
General Li Qi is fighting desperately,
holding the line!

25
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,590
Yan Xun is brazen enough

26
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,850
to use this as a pretext for war!

27
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,079
Your Majesty,

28
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:47,630
the situation is critical.

29
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:49,470
We don't know how much longer Li Qi can
hold the line.

30
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:51,270
Should we inform General Xiuli?

31
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,680
Qiao is exhausted.

32
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,680
Let her rest well.

33
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,470
We will

34
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,560
deal with Yan Xun.

35
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,840
This subject is willing to go to
Longyin Pass to reinforce General Li.

36
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,430
No.

37
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,310
The court has only just been stabilized.

38
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:06,400
You're responsible for
the defense of the capital.

39
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,960
Sending you now

40
00:03:08,110 --> 00:03:09,840
would undermine the stability of Tangjing.

41
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,840
But apart from me,

42
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,680
all the other generals
favor peace over war.

43
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,740
I fear that if such generals are sent,

44
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,750
the morale of the soldiers
on the front line will waver,

45
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,680
leaving them unable to resist
Great Yan's Black Eagle Army.

46
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,520
You may leave.

47
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,320
Let me think about it.

48
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,190
Right now, there is only one way

49
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,470
to solve your country's crisis:

50
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:50,530
reinforce General Li
and fight back against Great Yan.

51
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,640
I know that.

52
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:55,840
But I've just ascended the throne.

53
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:57,560
I have very few capable men
at my disposal.

54
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,750
Aside from Sun Di,

55
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,730
the other veteran generals

56
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,800
are all arrogant about their merits
and utterly obstinate.

57
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,080
Then let's make a deal.

58
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,630
I'll help you defeat Great Yan.

59
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:08,560
In return,

60
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,480
after Yan Xun retreats,

61
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,960
you have to lend me an army.

62
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,490
What do you need an army for?

63
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,100
I have my reasons.

64
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:18,760
You still have the nerve
to strike a deal with me?

65
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:23,190
Last time you promised me
the black gold mine.

66
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:23,720
To this day,

67
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,920
I haven't seen so much as a glimpse
of a gold nugget.

68
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,120
If not for you and Qiao saving me,

69
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,070
do you think I'd even be talking to you?

70
00:04:28,070 --> 00:04:29,070
Once it's done,

71
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,430
I'll return your men

72
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:32,070
and deliver 30% of the black gold mine

73
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:33,310
as agreed.

74
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:38,270
You're not planning to use my troops

75
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,420
to seize the black gold mine, are you?

76
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,330
None of your business.

77
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:49,430
Aren't you King Ximeng's double?

78
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,720
Could it be...

79
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,740
Could it be that in Ximeng, you're...

80
00:04:58,210 --> 00:04:58,940
I know!

81
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,240
You are nothing more than...

82
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,070
a puppet of King Ximeng.

83
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,920
I didn't expect your position in Ximeng

84
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,360
to be so dire.

85
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:15,990
Your Majesty guessed right.

86
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:18,000
Much like your own situation not long ago.

87
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:18,630
Zhuge Yue,

88
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:19,890
-You...
-Enough talk.

89
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:20,860
Do you

90
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:23,590
accept this deal or not?

91
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:36,310
I accept.

92
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,600
Where are you going, General Chu?

93
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,800
To the military camp.

94
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,680
General Chu.

95
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,630
I heard today is not a good day to go out.

96
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:48,680
Why don't you go another day?

97
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,680
Not a good day?

98
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:54,230
The heavens show unusual signs!

99
00:05:58,970 --> 00:06:00,480
Isn't the sun shining

100
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,860
and everything peaceful?

101
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:02,710
-General Chu,
-General Chu,

102
00:06:02,710 --> 00:06:04,000
-this is merely a false calm.
-this is merely a false calm.

103
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,170
-In an instant...
-In an instant...

104
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:05,790
The sky will darken.

105
00:06:05,790 --> 00:06:06,480
Winds will rise!

106
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:09,280
-A great storm will come!
-A great storm will come!

107
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,330
General Chu!

108
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,800
Song Cheng, the Imperial Guard,
pays respects to you.

109
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,740
I've come to present to you
the gifts bestowed by His Majesty.

110
00:06:18,740 --> 00:06:21,190
These are the gifts
His Majesty has prepared for you.

111
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,240
Thank you, Lord Song.

112
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,240
But I need to go to the military camp.

113
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:25,600
General Chu,

114
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:28,240
in addition to these gifts,
His Majesty has decreed

115
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,440
that starting today,

116
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,270
this mansion shall be officially renamed

117
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:32,680
the "General Xiuli's Mansion."

118
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:34,180
[General Xiuli's Mansion]

119
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,159
Lord Song,

120
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,750
please thank His Majesty for me.

121
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,270
But I really have urgent matters

122
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,750
and need to go to
the military camp in person.

123
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,880
So I won't go to the palace to thank him.

124
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,240
General Chu!

125
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:46,560
Today...

126
00:06:47,210 --> 00:06:48,610
is not a good day to go out.

127
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:52,230
The heavens show unusual signs.

128
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,630
The sky will darken,

129
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,480
winds will rise...

130
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,830
And a great storm is coming.

131
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,000
General Chu!

132
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:09,830
Your Highness,
congratulations on becoming General Xiuli.

133
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,830
Why don't we celebrate with a drink?

134
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:12,720
Yes.

135
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,360
Such a happy event—

136
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,160
we should celebrate it properly.

137
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,560
Are you two alright?

138
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:20,240
-The heavens show unusual signs.
-The heavens show unusual signs.

139
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,270
The sky will darken.

140
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,800
Winds will rise.

141
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,390
And a great storm is coming.

142
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:26,190
-Not a good day to go out!
-Not a good day to go out!

143
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:27,450
Not a good day to go out.

144
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:33,830
You've been doing everything you can
to stop me from going out.

145
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:35,830
What exactly are you hiding from me?

146
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,190
Xing,

147
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,680
come with me.

148
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:26,500
[Tangjing]

149
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,419
How can there be so many war refugees?

150
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,000
Open up.

151
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,000
What is it?

152
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,549
Behave!

153
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:44,770
Yan Xun's army has already
advanced to Longyin Pass.

154
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,720
Biantang's Yuncheng,
Xicheng, and Qiangcheng

155
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,120
have also been breached.

156
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,440
Right now, the officials are all saying

157
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,080
that this war started because of you

158
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,340
and have petitioned Li Ce to hand you over

159
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,020
to appease Great Yan's anger.

160
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,200
Li Ce wants to protect me.

161
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,360
But he shouldn't be stopping me.

162
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,420
I've already discussed it with Li Ce.

163
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:08,040
I'll fight this war for him.

164
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,550
Beat him!

165
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:21,270
Stop!

166
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:22,840
Stop it, all of you!

167
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,390
Stop!

168
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,770
Why are you hitting him?

169
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:29,080
Who are you? Mind your own business!

170
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,200
I am General Xiuli, Chu Qiao!

171
00:09:31,930 --> 00:09:33,150
Greetings, General Xiuli!

172
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:34,440
We didn't recognize you earlier,
General Chu.

173
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,550
Please forgive us.

174
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,320
This man stole the vendor's steamed buns,

175
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:39,030
which is why we were disciplining him.

176
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,760
General, please judge fairly.

177
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,060
What happened?

178
00:09:48,710 --> 00:09:49,590
General Xiuli,

179
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:52,030
it was him!
He stole my steamed buns first!

180
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,390
I'll buy all your buns.

181
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:08,040
Distribute them to the refugees here.

182
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,510
Okay, okay.

183
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,910
Thank you, General!

184
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:17,480
Here.

185
00:10:20,130 --> 00:10:21,530
Here. You must be hungry.

186
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:30,950
Why did he do that?

187
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:32,790
You are Chu Qiao?

188
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:34,530
It's all because of you

189
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,390
that Great Yan is attacking Biantang!

190
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,990
Because of you, we commoners

191
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:41,100
have lost our homes
and been forced to wander!

192
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,020
She is Chu Qiao!

193
00:10:43,050 --> 00:10:44,320
It's this woman!

194
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,550
She's the one who ruined our lives!

195
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:48,120
Kill this wicked woman!

196
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,200
Don't hurt them!

197
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,860
They have done nothing wrong!

198
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:55,440
Why is it so unacceptable

199
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:57,550
to send reinforcements to General Li?

200
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,350
Your Majesty,

201
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:00,390
the Black Eagle Army is unstoppable.

202
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:02,200
Our forces were completely unprepared

203
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,600
and unable to fight back.

204
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:05,870
If we rashly send reinforcements now,

205
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:08,030
we will only be sending more soldiers
to their deaths.

206
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:11,270
Moreover, the King of Great Yan's
true intention is not to conquer us.

207
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:13,030
If we send troops now,

208
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,550
there will be no room left

209
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:16,510
f-for negotiation between us.

210
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:17,870
In this time of national crisis,

211
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,960
Your Majesty must not let
matters of the heart cloud your judgment.

212
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,550
General Xiuli is righteous at heart—

213
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,270
surely she wouldn't wish
for our country to suffer.

214
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:25,030
The citizens of the realm come first.

215
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:26,390
Handing over General Chu

216
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,480
in exchange for peace
for the countless citizens—

217
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,150
General Chu will surely understand

218
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,720
Your Majesty's
well-intentioned consideration!

219
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,670
General Chu played a crucial role
in helping me ascend the throne.

220
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:35,910
If I abandon such a loyal official

221
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,630
in our hour of crisis,

222
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:40,220
do you want the whole world to ridicule me

223
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,750
for being heartless and ungrateful?

224
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,550
Your Majesty,

225
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:44,240
this subject has failed you.

226
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:46,970
I'm willing to
give everything for Your Majesty—

227
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,210
to die on the battlefield

228
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:50,550
and sacrifice my life without hesitation!

229
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:54,360
But I cannot gamble with
the lives of tens of thousands

230
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,480
of our soldiers!

231
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,200
I second that!

232
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:01,150
I second that!

233
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,180
I second that!

234
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:05,080
I second that!

235
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:27,600
Officials, you've been discussing
sending me off to Great Yan,

236
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,670
yet none of you thought to inform me,

237
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:30,270
the very person in question?

238
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:34,830
Your Majesty,

239
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,240
I have a gift

240
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,300
to present to the officials here.

241
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:40,170
Please go ahead, General Chu.

242
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,840
I, Chu Qiao,

243
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:50,390
have abducted all of your wives.

244
00:12:51,150 --> 00:12:51,840
What?

245
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,240
You...

246
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,550
T-This is outrageous!

247
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:58,190
Your Majesty,

248
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:00,150
General Xiuli has abducted
the families of court officials.

249
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,350
This is a grave crime!

250
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,080
Please uphold justice, Your Majesty!

251
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:05,510
How could you resort to
such despicable tactics?

252
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:07,240
Shameful! Outrageous!

253
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:07,970
General Chu,

254
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:12,510
that's my wife's coral hairpin, right?

255
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:13,840
I'm on your side.

256
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,830
Why did you take my wife too?

257
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,990
Please calm down, everyone.

258
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:18,720
I only wish

259
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:21,290
to make a point to His Majesty here.

260
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,910
I have no grudge whatsoever against
the wives of the officials present,

261
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:26,680
nor any intention of harming them.

262
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,920
I simply ask that you

263
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:31,750
cease submitting petitions to
send me to Great Yan as a hostage.

264
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:33,350
Despicable and ridiculous!

265
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,400
Your Majesty,

266
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:37,150
this matter concerns
the fate of our country.

267
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:39,270
For generations,
my family has been loyal to the country

268
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:40,600
through life and death!

269
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:43,270
I will never change my counsel
to the throne

270
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,840
because of my wife's safety.

271
00:13:46,270 --> 00:13:47,070
I second that.

272
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:48,600
The safety of one family
is a small matter—

273
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,240
the fate of Biantang is paramount!

274
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:52,150
How noble and righteous

275
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,080
you all are!

276
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,460
To die for His Majesty,

277
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,670
I will not hesitate!

278
00:13:56,670 --> 00:13:57,630
Well said!

279
00:13:58,550 --> 00:13:59,440
Officials,

280
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:02,350
if none of you would
change your political stance

281
00:14:02,350 --> 00:14:04,010
for the sake of your own wives,

282
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,310
then why do you believe

283
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:07,360
that the King of Great Yan

284
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:10,320
would stop the war for a woman like me?

285
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:15,170
What General Chu says
is precisely what I think.

286
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:17,750
Yan Xun is the King of Great Yan.

287
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:21,650
Back then, he fled back
to Great Yan all alone,

288
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,430
led the Black Eagle Army,

289
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,000
and conquered
half of Great Yong's territory.

290
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,130
That is proof enough

291
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,030
that he is a man

292
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:28,830
of both intellect and ambition.

293
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:32,150
Yuncheng, Xicheng, and Qiangcheng

294
00:14:32,430 --> 00:14:34,630
lie in Biantang's most fertile region.

295
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:35,960
Great Yan is harsh and barren.

296
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,320
By seizing these three cities,

297
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,520
they will establish their new granary.

298
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,390
Longyin Pass connects these three cities

299
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:42,910
and forms a defensive line.

300
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:44,390
It's both Biantang's strategic lifeline

301
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,240
and the shield protecting Great Yong.

302
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,600
If Longyin Pass falls,

303
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:50,450
the north of Biantang
will fall without a fight.

304
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:51,880
When the time comes,

305
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:54,390
if Yan Xun launches
a pincer attack on Great Yong,

306
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:56,120
it will be child's play for him.

307
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,570
Yan Xun is fiercely ambitious!

308
00:15:01,310 --> 00:15:02,160
Our Biantang

309
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,000
must not yield!

310
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:07,580
Please, Your Majesty, give the order

311
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:09,530
to appoint me as commander-in-chief

312
00:15:09,530 --> 00:15:10,790
to shoulder this burden on your behalf

313
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:12,510
and lead the campaign to Longyin Pass!

314
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,710
If I have not repelled

315
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:15,450
the Yan Army within one month,

316
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,410
I will leave Biantang on my own!

317
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,520
This campaign will be grueling.

318
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:37,810
I had not intended to trouble you with it.

319
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,840
Since Your Majesty has decided to fight,

320
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,440
I am willing to lead the army!

321
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:51,440
The General Xiuli's Mansion
is truly grand.

322
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,030
The garden alone

323
00:15:53,390 --> 00:15:54,960
is bigger than my house.

324
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,720
Duchess, Marchioness,

325
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,320
don't you think so?

326
00:15:59,630 --> 00:16:01,630
It's indeed grand!

327
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:03,270
Extremely grand.

328
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:04,440
Right?

329
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:09,170
[Xu Su's Wife]

330
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:07,840
General Chu hasn't been here very long,

331
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,170
yet she's put my home...

332
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:13,550
put all of our homes to shame.

333
00:16:13,810 --> 00:16:15,650
[Sun Di's Wife]

334
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,230
Mrs. Sun,

335
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:19,790
I don't think
your residence is this large, right?

336
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,120
Mrs. Xu,

337
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,450
that's quite a joke.

338
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:28,320
This residence used to be
the Crown Prince's mansion.

339
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:31,720
Its grandeur belongs to His Majesty.

340
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:34,510
How could our residences possibly compare?

341
00:16:34,510 --> 00:16:37,560
Could it be that you want to
outshine His Majesty?

342
00:16:37,650 --> 00:16:39,500
What are you talking about, Mrs. Sun?

343
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:41,500
How dare I compare with His Majesty?

344
00:16:52,030 --> 00:16:55,200
Today's grapes are so sour!

345
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,080
They're a hundred times

346
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:59,800
more sour than vinegar!

347
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,550
Try one.

348
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:05,720
It's quite sour.

349
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:06,960
Mrs. Xu,

350
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,440
have one too.

351
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:22,589
-What...
-Well...

352
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:23,400
Ladies,

353
00:17:23,589 --> 00:17:24,550
it's about time.

354
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:25,680
General Xiuli

355
00:17:25,710 --> 00:17:27,829
has prepared gifts for you in advance.

356
00:17:27,829 --> 00:17:29,360
Thank you for coming today.

357
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,700
The borrowed hairpins

358
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:33,050
will be sent to your residences tonight.

359
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:34,880
Honey!

360
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,640
Honey!

361
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:41,070
Where have you been all afternoon?

362
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:42,310
I couldn't find you anywhere.

363
00:17:42,310 --> 00:17:44,310
I just went to General Xiuli's mansion

364
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:45,350
for some tea.

365
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,510
The general even gave me a gift.

366
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:49,110
All your favorite pastries.

367
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,640
Tea?

368
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,660
When you were there,

369
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:55,060
did you sense any danger?

370
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:57,680
Or any hidden schemes or lurking threats?

371
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,960
What has gotten into you?

372
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:00,550
I just went to have some tea.

373
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:02,700
What could possibly have happened?

374
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:03,950
I was worried.

375
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,650
The situation has been unstable lately.

376
00:18:06,650 --> 00:18:08,450
I was concerned for your safety.

377
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:11,660
What is there to be so anxious about?

378
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:13,310
I came back perfectly fine, didn't I?

379
00:18:13,310 --> 00:18:14,570
Come on, let's go home.

380
00:18:14,570 --> 00:18:15,630
I was worried sick.

381
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,270
Xing.

382
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,210
What's this?

383
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:40,370
They're the Sun-Moon Twin Swords.

384
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:42,080
The sun represents you,

385
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,770
and the moon represents me.

386
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:49,990
Sun-Moon Twin Swords...

387
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,920
Is there anything special about them?

388
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:55,790
Our swords—the Fading Crimson Sword
and the Moon-breaking Sword—

389
00:18:55,790 --> 00:18:57,450
one fell into the frozen lake,

390
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:59,960
and the other was sent back
to Qingshan Manor.

391
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,400
I had them retrieved

392
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,800
through great hardship,

393
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:04,360
then melted down and forged

394
00:19:04,690 --> 00:19:06,010
into these two swords.

395
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:09,960
What else?

396
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:14,550
They represent

397
00:19:16,030 --> 00:19:17,830
that we will always be together.

398
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:21,790
You're not

399
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:24,400
just my Xing anymore.

400
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:27,070
You are General Xiuli—capable of
illuminating the path for many people.

401
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:29,110
These two swords and I

402
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:32,820
will accompany you
on the campaign to Longyin Pass,

403
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,140
fighting at your side.

404
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:14,920
Mr. Xiao,

405
00:20:15,830 --> 00:20:17,760
please give me some Huiyuan Pills.

406
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:21,620
Taking too many of those will kill you.

407
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:25,550
I must stay alive to
fight this battle through alongside Xing.

408
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,160
You must give them to me no matter what.

409
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:28,560
If General Chu finds out,

410
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,210
we'll both be finished.

411
00:20:30,690 --> 00:20:31,620
If I die,

412
00:20:32,140 --> 00:20:34,200
you may use my body for your research.

413
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:36,390
Really? You promise?

414
00:20:39,550 --> 00:20:41,190
W-What kind of person do you take me for?

415
00:20:41,190 --> 00:20:42,970
I would absolutely never agree
to something like this.

416
00:20:42,970 --> 00:20:43,580
I...

417
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:49,680
You...

418
00:20:50,790 --> 00:20:52,250
are not lying to me, right?

419
00:20:54,350 --> 00:20:55,000
No.

420
00:20:57,850 --> 00:20:58,850
No, no, no.

421
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:01,640
I would absolutely never agree
to something like this.

422
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,200
I-I am a person of principles!

423
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:03,590
Besides...

424
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:04,480
What if I give you

425
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,940
a reason you can't refuse?

426
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:08,480
This battle

427
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:10,720
concerns the lives of millions.

428
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:11,880
If we lose,

429
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:14,240
Biantang will be laid to ruin,

430
00:21:14,550 --> 00:21:16,550
with bodies strewn across the land.

431
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,780
There are four Huiyuan Pills inside.

432
00:21:25,710 --> 00:21:26,910
Take them sparingly.

433
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,090
If you take them all,

434
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,700
you'll really die.

435
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,740
You must remember,

436
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,170
if anything happens...

437
00:21:41,110 --> 00:21:41,720
Go.

438
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,400
Thank you, Mr. Xiao.

439
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:50,060
I've painstakingly hand-picked

440
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:52,140
these 20,000 elite soldiers myself.

441
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,920
You'd better count them carefully.

442
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,050
Elite soldiers?

443
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:57,640
From what I see, most of them

444
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,920
are disabled veterans

445
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,960
and untrained recruits.

446
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,070
General Chu,

447
00:22:03,070 --> 00:22:04,720
Biantang may be prosperous,

448
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,140
but we haven't fought

449
00:22:06,270 --> 00:22:08,310
a large-scale war in a long time.

450
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:09,880
This conflict arose suddenly,

451
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:11,830
so the troops we are able to
mobilize are limited.

452
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:14,400
You're the renowned General Xiuli,

453
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:16,750
who has won countless battles.

454
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:19,030
As long as you personally lead the army,

455
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:20,270
surely the Great Yan Army

456
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:22,200
will retreat without a fight.

457
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:23,200
Xu Su,

458
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:26,070
you're clearly trying to
sabotage the Xiuli Army!

459
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,270
Deputy Commander He,

460
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:29,070
I outrank you by two levels,

461
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:31,070
yet you dare address me by my name?

462
00:22:31,130 --> 00:22:32,650
That's insubordination!

463
00:22:33,030 --> 00:22:34,960
You'd better remember your place!

464
00:22:35,070 --> 00:22:36,830
You are Biantang's Xiuli Army,

465
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,640
not someone's private army!

466
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:42,590
His Majesty has arrived!

467
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,240
You may rise.

468
00:22:54,600 --> 00:22:55,230
Qiao,

469
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:58,580
I'm giving
these 3,000 imperial guards to you.

470
00:22:59,030 --> 00:23:00,290
These 3,000 guards are

471
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:02,910
the most elite force in all of Biantang.

472
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:05,200
They shall guard you and the people

473
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:08,790
of Longyin Pass as they would guard me.

474
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:10,150
Qiao,

475
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:11,880
you and the Xiuli Army

476
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:14,240
are the hope of Biantang.

477
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:17,670
Thank you, Your Majesty.

478
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:19,120
Get up quickly, Qiao.

479
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:28,000
March out!

480
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:48,750
[Tangjing]

481
00:24:07,850 --> 00:24:08,720
General Chu,
you must've had a long journey.

482
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:09,510
-General Chu.
-General Chu.

483
00:24:09,510 --> 00:24:11,110
General Li, you've worked hard.

484
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:11,840
General Chu,

485
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:13,030
we've been locked in this standoff

486
00:24:13,030 --> 00:24:14,760
with Great Yan for over a month.

487
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:16,830
Longyin Pass is easy to defend
and hard to attack,

488
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:18,200
but if this stalemate continues,

489
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,660
the garrison alone
won't be able to hold out.

490
00:24:21,110 --> 00:24:21,790
General Li,

491
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,160
I'll arrange for the Xiuli Army
to relieve your troops first,

492
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,440
so you can rest

493
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,990
and recover your strength.

494
00:24:27,350 --> 00:24:29,550
We'll follow your orders, General Chu!

495
00:24:52,550 --> 00:24:54,270
This wound has already begun to fester.

496
00:24:54,270 --> 00:24:56,070
It must be treated immediately.

497
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:58,310
This medicinal liquor is very strong.

498
00:24:58,310 --> 00:24:59,510
You'll need to endure some pain.

499
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:02,240
I've survived the blades
of Great Yan's savages.

500
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:03,440
What's

501
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,330
a little pain like this?

502
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,940
I'll come to remove
the bandages in three days.

503
00:25:16,940 --> 00:25:19,340
I must remove the pus
and dead tissue first.

504
00:25:24,950 --> 00:25:26,150
Thank you, thank you!

505
00:25:39,020 --> 00:25:40,110
It's getting cold.

506
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:42,560
In this environment, I'm afraid the wounds

507
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,180
may not heal properly.

508
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:45,680
Hurry.

509
00:25:49,870 --> 00:25:51,640
Add more charcoal every six hours

510
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,610
to maintain the temperature here.

511
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:53,810
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

512
00:26:07,840 --> 00:26:08,440
Look,

513
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:10,550
Longyin Pass is the gateway to Biantang.

514
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:11,750
If Great Yan wants to conquer Biantang,

515
00:26:11,750 --> 00:26:13,960
this place should've been
their first target.

516
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:15,640
But earlier, the Yan Army captured
three cities in succession,

517
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,830
taking a longer route

518
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:18,440
through the northeast of Biantang.

519
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:20,930
That's precisely because Longyin Pass is
shielded by mountains—

520
00:26:20,930 --> 00:26:21,830
easy to defend and hard to attack.

521
00:26:21,830 --> 00:26:22,480
So,

522
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:25,270
as long as we hold Longyin Pass,

523
00:26:25,270 --> 00:26:26,640
the Great Yan army
won't be able to hold out

524
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:27,830
and will retreat on its own.

525
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:28,480
Exactly.

526
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,600
General Chu, Lord Zhuge,

527
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:31,940
the battle for Longyin Pass

528
00:26:31,940 --> 00:26:33,680
won't be over anytime soon.

529
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:35,750
The military reports can wait.

530
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:37,200
Let's eat first.

531
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,000
Early this morning, he

532
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:39,510
went to the woods to hunt some game,

533
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:41,510
especially to nourish your health.

534
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,660
What are you saying?

535
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:52,120
Say that again!

536
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:53,400
Say that again!

537
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:54,030
Stop it!

538
00:26:54,930 --> 00:26:56,160
Come on! Still acting tough, huh?

539
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:57,310
Say that again if you dare!

540
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:58,270
What's going on here?

541
00:26:58,270 --> 00:26:59,160
General Chu,

542
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:01,050
they said we're useless freeloaders!

543
00:27:01,050 --> 00:27:02,310
You've been here for so many days,

544
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,360
yet you never go out to fight!

545
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:05,440
You said His Majesty
sent you to support us,

546
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,310
but what did you bring?

547
00:27:06,310 --> 00:27:07,790
Just your mouths!

548
00:27:08,050 --> 00:27:08,560
Exactly!

549
00:27:08,560 --> 00:27:10,160
You're eating our military rations!

550
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,270
If this drags on,

551
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:12,480
we won't even have enough food!

552
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,720
How are we supposed to defeat Great Yan?

553
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:14,830
How are we supposed to protect Biantang?

554
00:27:14,830 --> 00:27:16,200
How are we supposed to
protect His Majesty?

555
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:18,270
You are just useless freeloaders!

556
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,400
Say that again!

557
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:20,920
Say that again!

558
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:22,110
Stop!

559
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:24,750
You're totally useless!

560
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:25,550
He Xiao!

561
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:28,920
Has our grain supply still not arrived?

562
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:30,960
General Chu,

563
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:33,720
the supply convoy has somehow
been delayed for 10 days,

564
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:35,180
and there is still no news.

565
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,790
The grain we brought with the army

566
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:37,920
has long been used up.

567
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:40,320
We're indeed using General Li's supplies.

568
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:41,960
General Li was afraid you'd worry,

569
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:43,490
so he didn't let us tell you.

570
00:28:13,390 --> 00:28:14,020
Minglu,

571
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:16,970
have someone send
this dispatch out tonight.

572
00:28:16,970 --> 00:28:18,200
Make it extremely urgent.

573
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,720
We'll send out a dispatch every day

574
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:21,250
until the supplies arrive.

575
00:28:22,130 --> 00:28:22,760
Yes.

576
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:25,840
Shiyi.

577
00:28:28,550 --> 00:28:29,640
Yes, Young Master?

578
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:30,920
Tell me,

579
00:28:31,270 --> 00:28:33,590
how was this year's harvest in Great Yong?

580
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:35,440
Why are you asking that, Young Master?

581
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,270
Take this

582
00:28:36,270 --> 00:28:38,000
and go to the Qilin Bank
in Yancheng of Great Yong.

583
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:40,110
I have some land deeds and deposit slips
kept there.

584
00:28:40,110 --> 00:28:41,410
By any means necessary,

585
00:28:41,410 --> 00:28:44,160
procure provisions from Biantang
and Great Yong, regardless of cost.

586
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,350
As quickly as you can.

587
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:46,410
Yes, Young Master.

588
00:28:49,270 --> 00:28:50,930
How much grain is in this cart?

589
00:28:51,190 --> 00:28:52,680
Northern Biantang has experienced
heavy rains this year.

590
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:53,950
In the Red River Valley area,

591
00:28:53,950 --> 00:28:55,110
we encountered over 10 days of heavy rain,

592
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:56,190
which caused the delay.

593
00:28:56,190 --> 00:28:57,400
But rest assured, General Chu.

594
00:28:57,400 --> 00:28:58,660
His Majesty and Lord Xu

595
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:00,200
have personally instructed us.

596
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:02,400
There will be absolutely no problems
with the rations.

597
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,400
Have they all been counted clearly?

598
00:29:05,080 --> 00:29:06,280
Yes, no problem.

599
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:09,330
They've already been registered.

600
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:12,020
General Chu, this grain is not right!

601
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,040
General Chu.

602
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:21,270
What on earth is the meaning of this?

603
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:22,870
General Chu, why ask
when you already know the answer?

604
00:29:22,870 --> 00:29:24,000
Biantang has had a lot of rain this year.

605
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,190
The harvest was already poor.

606
00:29:25,190 --> 00:29:26,740
General Li Qi has been fighting

607
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:27,880
the Yan Army for months.

608
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:29,590
Now His Majesty has suddenly
ordered reinforcements.

609
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:30,830
That's 20,000 more mouths to feed.

610
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,590
Where can we get so much grain
on such short notice?

611
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:33,510
This is clearly Xu Su

612
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:36,840
deliberately making things difficult
for our General Chu!

613
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:39,740
Everyone, open the sacks
and inspect the grain!

614
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:45,370
It's all adulterated.

615
00:29:47,920 --> 00:29:48,640
Stop them!

616
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:49,750
Stop!

617
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,620
Seizing military grain
is a capital offense!

618
00:29:51,620 --> 00:29:52,690
Don't hurt them!

619
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,750
These are refugees who fled

620
00:30:01,750 --> 00:30:03,410
from the three fallen cities.

621
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:05,540
The Yan Army occupied the cities.

622
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,680
They have no food and no shelter.

623
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:10,160
They could only flee south,
beyond Longyin Pass.

624
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:11,400
Normally, during wartime,

625
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:12,480
refugees shouldn't
be allowed into the city—

626
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:14,810
that's the best policy to secure the rear.

627
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:16,490
General Li Qi couldn't bear it

628
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,940
and ordered that they not be driven away.

629
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:22,830
Take out my grain rations
and distribute them among the refugees.

630
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:23,830
From tomorrow on,

631
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:25,750
I'll eat with the soldiers.

632
00:30:26,270 --> 00:30:28,800
No more separate cooking
in the command tent.

633
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:32,340
Our intelligence reports

634
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:34,720
that Chu Qiao's troops
have been here for over 10 days,

635
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,050
yet she has made no move.

636
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:37,920
She must be planning to outlast us
in this stalemate.

637
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:39,720
I know how Chu conducts warfare.

638
00:30:40,370 --> 00:30:43,750
Given the current situation,
Biantang lies behind Longyin Pass.

639
00:30:43,750 --> 00:30:45,050
As long as they hold the pass,

640
00:30:45,050 --> 00:30:46,480
there's no need to deploy troops.

641
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:49,640
But the longer this drags on,
the more it works against us.

642
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:52,000
Spread word among the refugees
and civilians in Longyin Pass—

643
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:55,070
tell them that
as long as General Chu is willing to

644
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:56,310
surrender herself to Great Yan,

645
00:30:56,310 --> 00:30:58,070
Great Yan will withdraw its troops

646
00:30:58,070 --> 00:31:00,130
and leave them completely unharmed.

647
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,200
Cheng Yuan,

648
00:31:04,980 --> 00:31:06,950
you don't still think

649
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:11,110
I mobilized such a large army
to fight this war

650
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:13,240
just for Chu, do you?

651
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:16,440
I know Chu Qiao is only a pretext.

652
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:18,240
Your Majesty's real objective

653
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:21,880
is to seize the three granary cities
of Yuncheng, Xicheng, and Qiangcheng

654
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:22,830
from Biantang.

655
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,000
More than that,

656
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:26,480
once we take Longyin Pass,

657
00:31:26,790 --> 00:31:29,240
Biantang's forces will be driven south
of the Red River.

658
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,790
Then we can launch a pincer attack

659
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:32,520
and conquer Great Yong as well.

660
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:34,550
Your Majesty is wise.

661
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:45,880
Cheng Yuan.

662
00:31:49,350 --> 00:31:50,250
You and Chu

663
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:53,290
are both the most important people to me.

664
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:56,010
I hope you two
can get along in the future.

665
00:31:57,880 --> 00:32:00,920
I miss those days
after we left Zhenhuangcheng,

666
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:03,650
when you two were still my right-hand men.

667
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:08,680
Back then,
the Black Eagle Army was unstoppable.

668
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:11,160
We came so close

669
00:32:12,430 --> 00:32:16,360
to breaking through Great Yong's
final line of defense several times.

670
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:19,110
Your Majesty,

671
00:32:19,210 --> 00:32:19,920
there will surely come a day

672
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,780
when we truly conquer Great Yong.

673
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,000
What do you think you're doing?

674
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,000
You can't gather here!

675
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:46,650
We want to see General Chu!

676
00:32:46,670 --> 00:32:48,000
We want to see General Chu!

677
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,680
We won't leave until we see General Chu!

678
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,030
We won't leave until we see her!

679
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:52,640
Let us see General Chu!

680
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:54,070
Please let us see General Chu!

681
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:55,530
We want to see General Chu!

682
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:02,150
It's getting colder now.

683
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:04,600
Biantang soldiers aren't used to the cold.

684
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:05,430
If we don't solve

685
00:33:05,430 --> 00:33:07,350
the problem of
provisions and military supplies,

686
00:33:07,350 --> 00:33:08,400
I'm afraid

687
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:10,640
we may collapse before Great Yan does.

688
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:12,270
Yue Shiyi just returned yesterday.

689
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:14,270
He's procured 500 dans of provisions
from southern Great Yong

690
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,680
and eastern Biantang.

691
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:17,400
No matter what,

692
00:33:17,550 --> 00:33:18,750
we can get through the next few days.

693
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:19,480
General Chu!

694
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,240
He Xiao.

695
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,400
What's wrong?

696
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:24,080
Yan Xun has spread word inside the pass

697
00:33:24,080 --> 00:33:25,750
that as long as you
are willing to surrender,

698
00:33:25,750 --> 00:33:27,020
he will withdraw his troops immediately.

699
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:27,630
Now, outside the camp,

700
00:33:27,630 --> 00:33:30,430
crowds of civilians
are demanding you surrender.

701
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,640
It's General Chu.

702
00:33:41,010 --> 00:33:42,210
General Chu has come!

703
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:43,800
General Chu has come.

704
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:44,900
She's here!

705
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,240
General Chu!

706
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:48,030
General Chu, save us!

707
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:49,870
General Chu, please save us!

708
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:50,830
General Chu!

709
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:51,750
Please save us!

710
00:33:51,750 --> 00:33:52,680
Everyone, please don't kneel!

711
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:53,640
Get up quickly!

712
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:54,400
General Chu,

713
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:55,810
the King of Great Yan said

714
00:33:55,810 --> 00:33:56,920
that as long as you go with him,

715
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,920
he will withdraw.

716
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:01,460
Please, save us.

717
00:34:01,750 --> 00:34:02,750
General Chu,

718
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:04,160
I'm from Shenzhou.

719
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:08,280
My daughter and uncle
are still in Shenzhou.

720
00:34:08,550 --> 00:34:11,400
I don't know if they are dead or alive.

721
00:34:11,830 --> 00:34:13,380
Please,

722
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:15,070
General Chu!

723
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,800
I kowtow to you!

724
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:17,510
Granny,

725
00:34:17,510 --> 00:34:18,550
please get up!

726
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,880
General Chu, please

727
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:22,110
save us!

728
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:26,030
Please save us, General Chu!

729
00:34:31,690 --> 00:34:33,810
Stop begging her, everyone!

730
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,590
A woman like her

731
00:34:35,760 --> 00:34:37,670
doesn't care if we live or die!

732
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,880
Look at what she is wearing,

733
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:42,030
and look at what we're wearing!

734
00:34:42,510 --> 00:34:43,739
She's got our Emperor

735
00:34:43,770 --> 00:34:45,860
completely under her spell!

736
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:47,320
Even the King of Great Yan

737
00:34:47,510 --> 00:34:49,100
is captivated by her!

738
00:34:49,190 --> 00:34:51,070
As long as we offer her
to the King of Great Yan,

739
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:52,320
we'll all be saved!

740
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:53,560
Seize her!

741
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:57,390
All of you, step back!

742
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,150
Step back!

743
00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,190
Step back!

744
00:34:59,190 --> 00:35:00,150
What are you doing?

745
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:00,880
What are you doing?

746
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:02,000
Don't come forward anymore!

747
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:02,800
Get back now!

748
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:20,320
Yan,

749
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:23,010
I don't have much time left.

750
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:25,550
Now I tell you the truth

751
00:35:26,240 --> 00:35:28,920
because you have the right
to know your origins.

752
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:31,630
I was born into the royal family

753
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:35,590
and was drawn into
far too many struggles for power.

754
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,190
I also know full well

755
00:35:38,190 --> 00:35:40,880
that the truth will only bring you
more pain.

756
00:35:41,590 --> 00:35:42,190
You,

757
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:43,590
I,

758
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:46,280
and even your birth mother—

759
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:48,150
the Empress—

760
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:51,420
none of us could do anything about it.

761
00:35:52,370 --> 00:35:53,370
All we can do

762
00:35:53,390 --> 00:35:56,510
is take this secret with us
as we grow old—

763
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,360
and into the grave.

764
00:36:05,110 --> 00:36:05,970
Your Highness.

765
00:36:06,070 --> 00:36:06,670
Matron,

766
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:09,030
is Her Majesty still unwilling to see me?

767
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,890
Her Majesty has agreed to see you.

768
00:36:10,890 --> 00:36:11,890
But...

769
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:13,110
But what?

770
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:15,760
Her Majesty is not feeling well.

771
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:19,420
After Your Highness pays your respects,
you should leave early.

772
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,520
Don't worry, Matron.

773
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:24,160
I'll leave
as soon as I've paid my respects.

774
00:36:40,110 --> 00:36:42,920
I, Li Yan, pay my respects
to Your Majesty.

775
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:47,180
By your decree,
I remained in Jincheng

776
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:49,530
for three years to guard my father's tomb.

777
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:51,670
Now that I've just returned to Tangjing,

778
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:53,130
I came specifically to...

779
00:36:54,350 --> 00:36:56,210
to pay my respects to Your Majesty

780
00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:58,250
and to thank you for your care.

781
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,600
You came all the way to see me—

782
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:03,170
surely not merely to show gratitude.

783
00:37:05,550 --> 00:37:08,480
What did the Prince of Chang say to you
before he died?

784
00:37:10,230 --> 00:37:11,690
Raise your head and speak.

785
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,880
Before my father died, he told me...

786
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:25,760
He said...

787
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:28,550
He said I'm actually

788
00:37:28,550 --> 00:37:29,550
Your Majesty's...

789
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,190
Li Yan!

790
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:45,510
What your father said is not important.

791
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:49,590
Your father was
the late Prince of Chang of Jincheng.

792
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:52,480
His Majesty,
honoring the brotherhood between them

793
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,540
and considering you are his only son,

794
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:57,110
made an exception and appointed you
a commandery prince.

795
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,030
Who you are—

796
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:00,760
don't you know it yourself?

797
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:02,830
Your Majesty,

798
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:05,220
I don't understand what you mean.

799
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:07,760
I know why you've been seeking an audience

800
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:09,510
with me day after day

801
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:11,400
since your return from Jincheng.

802
00:38:12,670 --> 00:38:13,480
Your Majesty, I...

803
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,670
I agreed to see you

804
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:16,900
because I want to tell you something.

805
00:38:17,590 --> 00:38:18,990
In this imperial palace,

806
00:38:20,070 --> 00:38:20,760
power,

807
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:22,000
titles,

808
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:23,750
and His Majesty's favor—

809
00:38:24,510 --> 00:38:25,840
every single one of them

810
00:38:26,030 --> 00:38:27,880
is more important than blood ties.

811
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,540
When the Prince of Chang died,

812
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:32,370
I had you guard his tomb
in Jincheng for three years

813
00:38:32,370 --> 00:38:33,190
because I hoped you would use

814
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:35,450
that time to think this through clearly.

815
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,000
Did His Majesty

816
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:40,160
and the late Crown Prince Maocheng

817
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:42,360
not share blood ties?

818
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:45,080
But what happened in the end?

819
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:56,070
I, Li Yan, will heed
Your Majesty's teachings

820
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,070
and keep

821
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,360
your words in mind.

822
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:02,960
Your Majesty, I...

823
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:03,690
Attendants!

824
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,400
Escort the Prince of Luo out.

825
00:39:35,030 --> 00:39:36,360
What my mother has lost,

826
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:39,280
I will win back for her.

827
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:47,660
Your Highness!

828
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:58,710
Your Highness.

829
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,880
Only one little Heir Apparent?

830
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:29,550
Yes,

831
00:40:30,030 --> 00:40:31,320
only one.

832
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:33,300
Wait outside for a moment.

833
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:35,560
The weather has turned cold today.

834
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:38,880
The little Heir Apparent needs
an additional layer of clothing

835
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:40,080
lest he catch a chill.

836
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:40,880
Yes.

837
00:41:03,030 --> 00:41:03,830
Your Majesty.

838
00:41:11,250 --> 00:41:12,050
Your Majesty,

839
00:41:12,240 --> 00:41:13,480
why did you hand the Prince of Chang's son

840
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,550
to that matron?

841
00:41:43,480 --> 00:41:44,280
Zhuge Yue,

842
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,670
you and I are different.

843
00:41:45,670 --> 00:41:47,870
There has always been a gulf between us.

844
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:49,020
Chu...

845
00:41:50,630 --> 00:41:52,800
Since he chose to leave first,

846
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:55,710
it means he's found something
more important.

847
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:58,070
Chu,

848
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:00,200
no matter where you run,

849
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:01,960
I will find you.

850
00:42:02,150 --> 00:42:02,960
Zhuge Yue,

851
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:05,800
when you wake up, forget about me.

